data.description:
Discover Riverside Bliss: 3BR, 2BA Home with Scenic Muskingum River Views

Indulge in the epitome of picture-perfect living with this captivating 3-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled along the Muskingum River. Every detail of this residence is designed for comfort and style, featuring brand-new flooring that adds a touch of modern elegance.

Step inside to an amazing open floorplan that seamlessly blends functionality and aesthetics. The heart of this home is a haven for gathering and entertaining. A newly built (2021) 42x30 2+ car detached garage with an additional workshop provides ample space for your projects and storage needs, while a convenient carport ensures hassle-free parking.

As you step onto the deck, be prepared to be mesmerized by the Muskingum River frontage, creating a serene backdrop for relaxation and enjoyment. Picture yourself unwinding on summer nights, taking in the breathtaking views and embracing the myriad of entertaining opportunities this property presents.

Key Features:

3 bedrooms, 2 baths - a perfect blend of space and comfort.
All-new flooring for a contemporary and fresh ambiance.
Expansive open floorplan - ideal for seamless living and entertaining.
2+ car detached garage with a workshop and a convenient carport.
Muskingum River frontage, offering a tranquil setting and stunning views.
A deck overlooking the river - a perfect spot to relax and recharge.
Fall in love with the charm and allure of this riverfront property. Experience the luxury of riverside living and create lasting memories in a home where tranquility meets entertainment. Don't miss the chance to make this your own personal retreat!
